course_name: Introduction to Computer Programming in Java
course_description:
Introduction to computer programming and to problem solving techniques using computer programs; programming lab experience.
Prereq: Math 1130, 1140, 1149, 1150, or 1151, or Math Placement Level L. This course is available for EM credit.
